. تجديد البشرة، اضطرابات فرط الصتبغ، ندبات</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">كربوكسي للهالات السوداء وعلامات التمدد. شد البشرة وعلاج الندبات</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">العلاج بالضوء.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">الناروباند </span><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">UVB</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">اكزيمر ليزر</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">حقن البوتوكس. إعادة النضارة، علاج التجاعيد وشد الوجه، وفرط التعرق.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">حقن الفيلر: علاج التجاعيد وشد الوجه واليدين والرقبة.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">حقن البلازما الغنية بالصفائح الدموية.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">شد الوجه. طريقة غير جراحية لشد الوجه</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt -3.05pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Sakkal Majalla\';\">- </span></strong><strong><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">التجميل بالإبر.</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=