 the treatment of obesity of all kinds.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The causes and types of obesity differ, and with that, the methods of diagnosis and treatment are different. Therefore, because obesity treatment is a distinct medical subspecialty, we were keen at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital to establish an integrated medical team to reach an accurate medical diagnosis of the condition and thus a successful and effective treatment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The team is equipped with anesthesiologists, endocrinologists, psychiatrists, gastroenterologists, and other distinguished specialists, who work in operating rooms equipped with the latest medical devices in the field of stapling and endoscopy.</span></p>','2021-01-01 15:21:09','2021-01-01 15:21:09'),(604,'services','title',11,'en','Women\'s Health Center','2021-01-01 15:29:10','2021-01-01 15:29:10'),(605,'services','slug',11,'en','women-s-health-center','2021-01-01 15:29:10','2021-01-01 15:29:10'),(606,'services','content',11,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">At Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, we care about women and take care of them, so we set up a special section for them on their health.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>We provide her with reliable medical advice in everything related to women\'s health, from infertility and r