rn technologies, and integrated programs in the field of patient care, prevention, and health education.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">At the center, we provide all services related to cancer, <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">including</strong>:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; General check-ups and comprehensive care for cancer diseases in the outpatient department.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Inpatient long-term chemotherapy injection (requires only one night\'s sleep in hospital).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; Rapid chemotherapy injections and blood transfusions (performed in an outpatient short-stay unit).</span></p>','2021-01-01 15:46:59','2021-01-01 15:46:59'),(619,'services','title',16,'en','Gastroenterology Center','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(620,'services','slug',16,'en','gastroenterology-center','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(621,'services','content',16,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In the Gastroenterology Center, we provide integrated medical care for patients, starting with the proper diagnosis of the situation and taking a history of it, through diagnosis using modern and advanced medical devices.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Then treatment according to organized, detailed, comprehensive treatment plans for the appropriate medication and appropriate medical intervention, in addition to periodic follow-up of the case continuously, leading to the patient\'s complete recovery and return to normal life.</span></p>','2021-01-01 15:52:13','2021-01-01 15:52:13'),(622,'services','title',17,'en','Nephrology and Dialysis Center','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-01-01 15:58:53'),(623,'services','slug',17,'en','nephrology-and-dialysis-center','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-01-01 15:58:53'),(624,'services','content',17,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Department of Kidney Diseases and Dialysis at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital contains numerous modern medical devices related to the field.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;The most prominent of which is the (BBRAUN Dialog) devices, which are considered one of the best and most modern dialysis techniques in the world, as they are characterized by high efficiency, ease of use, and complete safety. They are also equipped with a large screen that monitors all indicators during the washing session, including the indicator for automatic blood pressure measurement.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">This new generation of hemodialysis machines is characterized by its ability to measure the dialysis dose throughout the treatment period, with advanced technologies that enable the doctor to define and adjust the treatment parameters precisely, which helps to reach the maximum effectiveness of dialysis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">BBRAUN works with a new method called Hemodiafiltration via the Internet, which removes toxins and large particles from the blood, which was impossible to do with traditional dialysis methods.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In addition, the center contains other advanced devices such as CRRT devices, which are among the latest technologies for kidney replacement.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">These devices can wash the kidneys of patients who suffer from severe diseases in the intensive care unit, such as low blood pressure and sepsis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It is also worth noting that the dialysis unit at Al-Moosa Hospital is one of the largest units in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, as it contains 30 dialysis machines with a capacity of 120 patients. Each patient has a unique space to ensure privacy and reduce the possibility of infection.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The dialysis unit is based on a team of skilled consultants and specialists in nephrology and dialysis. We also have in the unit a professional technical staff and nurses who are fully trained in the field of dialysis.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;We strive to achieve the principle of comprehensive medical care that makes the patient the focus of his attention, and from here, we have provided the center with clinical dietitians and social workers who collaborate in one team.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The team is tasked with making the rounds to provide patients with necessary information about their diet and to support them socially and psychologically.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">The hospital gives priority to hemodialysis patients, as it provides them with dedicated parking in the basement and provides them with private car transportation from their homes to the hospital for free. Finally, we hope that the dialysis unit, with its modern, advanced equipment and integrated staff, will be a distinctive mark and a qualitative addition in the field of dialysis patient care in the eastern region of the Kingdom.</span></p>','2021-01-01 15:58:53','2021-01-01 15:58:53'),(625,'services','title',18,'en','Pediatric Center','2021-01-01 16:02:50','2021-01-01 16:02:50'),(626,'services','slug',18,'en','pediatric-center','2021-01-01 16:02:50','2021-01-01 16:02:50'),(627,'services','content',18,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Children are the bright side in the life of parents; it is around them that the lives and concerns of the p