erventions, such as:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Trancatheter Aortic Valve Implantation (TAVI).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The use of the Rot ablator device: through this device, the most difficult cases of hardening of the coronary arteries and the deposition of fat in them are dealt with, to break up fats and other deposits through the catheter without the need for surgical intervention.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The latest methods of treating heart rhythm disturbances through catheters in the Cardiac Physiology and Electrophysiology Laboratory equipped with the latest medical devices</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Implantation of advanced pacemakers to treat irregular heartbeat and achieve a stable and stable state of the heart</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Remember that, at Al-Moosa Specialist Center, we care about all the details of our patients and their families, we always give their comfort the priority, and we constantly strive to provide the best medical service, to keep pace with science and be a soothing condition for people\'s diseases!</span></p>','2021-01-01 16:51:21','2021-01-01 16:51:21'),(664,'service_sections','title',8,'en','Neurosurgery','2021-01-01 16:52:49','2021-01-01 16:52:49'),(665,'service_sections','title',9,'en','Nerve Diseases','2021-01-01 16:53:35','2021-01-01 16:53:35'),(666,'service_sections','title',10,'en','Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory','2021-01-01 16:55:29','2021-01-01 16:55:29'),(667,'service_sections','title',11,'en','Mental health and Psychology','2021-01-01 16:56:52','2021-01-01 16:56:52'),(668,'service_sections','title',12,'en','Why choose our center?','2021-01-01 16:59:27','2021-01-01 16:59:27'),(669,'service_sections','title',13,'en','Our Mission','2021-01-01 17:00:15','2021-01-01 17:00:15'),(670,'service_sections','title',14,'en','Our Vision','2021-01-01 17:00:57','2021-01-01 17:00:57'),(671,'service_section_items','title',12,'en','Neurosurgery','2021-01-01 17:03:08','2021-01-01 17:03:08'),(672,'service_section_items','content',12,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">We perform various types of surgeries for the central, peripheral, and spine nervous system.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Our center offers a comprehensive range of procedures and surgeries for patients suffering from disorders that fall within the department\'s services.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>The center also treats some pediatric and newborn disorders, which include (hydrocephalus, spine bifida, and other congenital anomalies that affect the nervous system.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>In addition to post-traumatic conditions including head injuries, spinal injuries, and peripheral nerve injuries, as well as brain and spine tumors, deformities and degenerative diseases and (scoliosis, kyphosis) of the spine, as well as brain and spine deformities, they are some of the most treated disorders in the center.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We also exceed at our center by assessing the need and benefit of surgical intervention in epilepsy patients.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Some cases cannot be treated surgically after studying them, while some cases can be operated on.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:03:08','2021-01-01 17:03:08'),(673,'service_section_items','title',13,'en','Nerve Diseases','2021-01-01 17:04:50','2021-01-01 17:04:50'),(674,'service_section_items','content',13,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">To ensure the provision of high-quality healthcare services to all neurological patients, our outpatient team works with utmost enthusiasm and dedication with patients, their families, and workers in other departments, to provide a patient-centered health service.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Our services are based on evidence through continuous assessment of the patient, with the aim of effectively assisting him in treating and managing his health condition.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The outpatient neurology unit cares for patients with diseases of the brain, spinal cord, peripheral nerves, and muscles who require comprehensive evaluation and regular care.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">In addition, the services provided by the outpatient clinics to patients are based on the appointment system, in addition to direct attendance to the center in case of patients in need of urgent referrals.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The consultants in our clinic provide diagnostic evaluation and consultations for the treatment of neurobehavioral and memory disorders, neuromuscular diseases, cardiovascular and movement disorders, headaches, seizures, sleep disorders (obstructive sleep apnea - insomnia), brain tumors, and headaches. In addition, many diseases, such as Alzheimer\'s and multiple sclerosis, have molecular immunity. Neurology receives a great deal of attention, good and compassionate care within our center.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:04:50','2021-01-01 17:04:50'),(675,'service_section_items','title',14,'en','Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory','2021-01-01 17:07:38','2021-01-01 17:07:38'),(676,'service_section_items','content',14,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Neurophysiology Diagnostic Laboratory</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Neurophysiology is primarily an investigative (diagnostic) discipline that uses computers, electrical, magnetic, and electronic means to record the function of the brain, spinal cord, spinal cord roots, peripheral nerves, and muscles to diagnose functional disorders of the nervous system. These technologies include:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>EEG.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Electromyography.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Nerve conduction study.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Monitoring during operations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Evoked potential.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Monitoring during operations:</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It is used for monitoring during surgical procedures to reduce the incidence of neurological diseases during surgical treatments. The goal of this monitoring is to identify changes in the brain, spinal cord, and peripheral nerve function before hard-to-repair damage occurs.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>It is also effective in positioning anatomical structures including peripheral nerves and the sensorimotor cortex, which helps to guide surgeons during autopsies. Surgical procedures using this technique include scoliosis surgery, carotid endarterectomy, and brain resection surgery.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:07:38','2021-01-01 17:07:38'),(677,'service_section_items','title',15,'en','Mental health and Psychology','2021-01-01 17:13:54','2021-01-01 17:13:54'),(678,'service_section_items','content',15,'en','<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Psychiatry Clinics:</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The psychiatric clinic at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital is considered one of the oldest and most important psychotherapy clinics in private hospitals at Al-Ahsa level. For nearly 15 years, we have been providing treatment to patients from different parts of the Eastern Region and outside as well.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Department of Psychiatry is pleased to provide psychological counseling, treat all behavioral and psychological disorders, and solve any psychological problem that may face us at any stage and under any circumstance that we face in our life, as we provide psychological and social support through a consultant specialized in psychiatry with a high degree of competence and has long experience In this area.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Department of Psychiatry, God willing, treats all cases of anxiety, fear, or depression, as well as panic attacks, obsessive-compulsive disorder, sleep or eating disorders such as increased or decreased appetite, or treatment of physical symptoms without an organic cause such as irritable bowel syndrome, migraine attacks, total or hair loss because most of them are Be psychological.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Also, the Department of Psychiatry treats children who suffer from psychological diseases or disorders such as autism, learning difficulties, hyperactivity, distractibility, slurred speech or involuntary urination, or it provides some therapeutic rehabilitation for children and if you have one of the parents suffering from a psychotic disorder such as schizophrenia or volatility Bipolar or a parent with dementia or Alzheimer\'s.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Likewise, the department includes psychologist clinics to provide evaluation, treatment and follow-up services from the use of IQ testing and psychological tests for children and adults, as well as providing psychological analytical therapy and cognitive-behavioral therapy sessions.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The psychiatric clinics team at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital consists of:</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Consultants in diseases and mental disorders.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Psychologists.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-Social service.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depression Treatment Program</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depression is considered one of the most common psychological disorders in the world, and it is divided into two main types: depressive disorders and anxiety disorders. This disease is spread widely across the globe and greatly affects the mood and feeling of people affected by it. Symptoms of depression vary according to its severity (from mild to severe) and according to the duration of the episode.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It is (from months to years), and it can be easily diagnosed, and it is worth for us to know that it differs from the normal feeling of sadness.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">And the stress, and fear that afflicts every human being from time to time in life.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">At the global level, 300 million people suffer from depression, representing 4.4% of the world\'s population, and this is a relatively high percentage. Although depression may affect people of all ages and groups, the risk of developing it is:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It increases significantly in the event of poverty, unemployment, or upon the advent of calamities and traumatic events such as the death of a close or loved one, or when</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Divorce, physical illness, or problems that may be caused by drug and alcohol use.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">In the Psychiatry Clinic at Al Musa Specialized Hospital, we offer the complete program and effective treatment plans to control and treat </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Depressive disorders, including:</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- A complete evaluation and diagnosis of the health and psychological condition.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Tests that would exclude the organic causes of depression. -</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- A treatment program developed after a long discussion and dialogue with the patient, and it consists of a treatment plan that uses a drug approach.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Others use psychological therapy (through a cognitive behavioral therapy program or psychological analysis).</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The causes and symptoms of all these diseases and mental disorders have become well known, as well as knowing what happens to the brain from chemical changes in neurotransmitters in every mental illness with the creation of multiple and advanced psychological drugs with an excellent positive effect and avoiding side effects to the maximum degree. All this led to a positive surge in the treatment of most Mental illnesses during this period, mental illnesses have become like other organic diseases have their treatments, and thus man lives far from suffering and psychological headache, so there is no need to hesitate, the door is open to return to a life of happiness and hope, God willing.</span></p>','2021-01-01 17:13:54','2021-01-04 15:18:24'),(679,'service_section_items','title',16,'en','Why Choose Our Center? ','2021-01-01 17:17:31','2021-01-01 17:17:31'),(680,'service_section_items','c