 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The Eye Center crews at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital take good care of your eyes. Our teams are known for their high efficiency, long experience, and full care for patient comfort.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>In addition to our modern equipment that keeps pace with the latest in modern medical science, so do not hesitate to visit us and take reliable medical advice.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Always make sure that our attention to simple details is what makes Al Moosa Specialist Hospital special!</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:19:22','2021-01-01 18:19:22'),(727,'service_sections','title',29,'en','Laparoscopic Gastric Bypass Surgery','2021-01-01 18:21:37','2021-01-01 18:21:37'),(728,'service_sections','title',30,'en','Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy','2021-01-01 18:22:59','2021-01-01 18:22:59'),(729,'service_sections','title',31,'en','Converting from Sleeve Gastrectomy to Laparoscopic Graft','2021-01-01 18:24:00','2021-01-01 18:24:00'),(730,'service_sections','title',32,'en','Removing a stomach belt (ring) and converting to a sleeve gastrectomy or bypass','2021-01-01 18:24:46','2021-01-01 18:24:46'),(731,'service_section_items','title',33,'en','Laparoscopic Gastric Bypass Surgery','2021-01-01 18:26:01','2021-01-01 18:26:01'),(732,'service_section_items','content',33,'en','<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">It is one of the most popular and effective procedures in the treatment of obesity, which helps