n: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>It is recommended for men to shorten the hair and trim the beard in the desired places.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Do not use gels and sprays on hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>For women, do not apply the gel, hair sprays, or henna.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The examination ends at 5:30 a.m., and you must arrange transportation after discharge from the hospital before coming to the center.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>If you feel tired or have the flu, you must inform the department at least the day before the examination and reschedule your appointment: Call 0135369666 Ext: 1298.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt .5in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&middot;<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong>Caution</strong>: Failure to comply with the aforementioned instructions may cause the test to fail and difficulty obtaining real results.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>','2021-01-01 18:52:26','2021-01-01 18:52:26'),(755,'service_section_items','title',42,'en','Sleep Check','2021-01-01 18:53:19','2021-01-01 18:53:19'),(756,'service_section_items','content',42,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">During the examination, the sleep laboratory technician puts sensors on different places of the body, such as the head, face, chest, abdomen, and legs, as the sleep disorder device records and measures electrical waves of the brain, breathing movements, oxygen level in the blood and heartbeats, while recording and photographing all limb movements through a high-resolution camera.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>This is done without any pain, the patient stays in a comfortable private room closest to the bedrooms, with all the amenities and public safety, and spends his sleep hours from ten in the evening until the morning, and sometimes some tests may need to be done in the morning period.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-01 18:53:19','2021-01-01 18:53:19'),(757,'service_sections','title',39,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 18:54:16','2021-01-01 18:54:16'),(758,'service_section_items','title',43,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-01 18:55:52','2021-01-01 18:55:52'),(759,'service_section_items','content',43,'en','<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">&bull; Rooms for urgent and unexpected deliveries: designed in a way that takes into account the speed of the situation and the immediate response to the situation</span>