mbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Growth hormone problems.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:27:09','2021-01-01 22:27:09'),(865,'service_section_items','title',78,'en','Patient Medical Awareness','2021-01-01 22:28:38','2021-01-01 22:28:38'),(866,'service_section_items','content',78,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Awareness is considered one of the most successful methods in confronting disease, as the information the patient possesses is always his strongest weapon in dealing with the disease</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">When you visit Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, you will know everything you need to know about your health condition, and you will receive the necessary training and education about the optimal healthy diet, how to maintain your physical activity, monitor blood sugar level, and ways to take treatment. In addition to all the information and skills that would ensure you a happy life free from the risk of complications from diabetes, to have a comfortable life free from any health problems!</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:28:38','2021-01-01 22:28:38'),(867,'services','title',27,'en','Hair Transplant Center ','2021-01-01 22:32:45','2021-01-01 22:32:45'),(868,'services','slug',27,'en','hair-transplant-center','2021-01-01 22:32:45','2021-01-01 22:32:45'),(869,'services','excerpt',27,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Hair problems and hair loss are among the common problems globally in the modern era. The reasons may differ, which may be hereditary or due to the excessive use of hair products and creams.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:32:45','2021-01-01 22:32:45'),(870,'services','content',27,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Hair problems and hair loss are among the common problems globally in the modern era. The reasons may differ, which may be hereditary or due to the excessive use of hair products and creams.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Later on, hair loss may lead to psychological problems, especially among young people, and they enter into bouts of depression due to their loss of hair, which used to give them distinction among their peers.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">We, at The Hair Transplant Center inside Al Mousa Specialist Hospital, offer a very high-quality hair transplant service. We are through our cooperation with Dr. Arpichi from the famous Turkish Prime Clinic who has long experience in the field of hair transplantation. He has performed more than 5000 hair transplants in the past 13 years.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>We seek to raise the quality of our service provided to the pioneers of our center in the Kingdom, through networking and constant access to the most prominent technologies reached by modern science in the field of hair transplantation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">In our center, we rely on the latest medical technologies in the field, as we rely on the technique of hair follicle extraction unit (FUE), which allows surgeons to pull hair follicles from the back of the head and then implant them in areas of baldness and hair loss.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:32:45','2021-01-01 22:32:45'),(871,'services','title',28,'en','Stroke Program','2021-01-01 22:37:10','2021-01-01 22:37:10'),(872,'services','slug',28,'en','stroke-program','2021-01-01 22:37:10','2021-01-01 22:37:10'),(873,'services','excerpt',28,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The defining and critical moments in the life of the patient are the first moments of getting a stroke, and his awareness of the importance of knowing an early diagnosis and timely care is his strongest weapon in interacting with this condition, otherwise the stroke can triumph over it, leading to life-long complications.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:37:11','2021-01-01 22:37:11'),(874,'services','content',28,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The defining and critical moments in the life of the patient are the first moments of getting a stroke, and his awareness of the importance of knowing an early diagnosis and timely care is his strongest weapon in interacting with this condition, otherwise the stroke can triumph over it, leading to life-long complications.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">We, in the Stroke Program at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, care about these defining moments and give them our greatest attention, from the first moments of entering the emergency department or the rest of the stroke-related departments, to the Department of Neurology and Neurosurgery and Vascular, through the final stages of physical therapy, rehabilitation and care With mental health, accurate and continuous follow-up of the patient, and providing medical advice to those who have previously had a stroke, in pursuit of a comprehensive and accurate management of stroke and its symptoms.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">We also aim to inform patients and help individuals to know risk factors and early signs of a stroke, and to contact KSA 997 immediately when any symptoms of stroke occur, in our belief in the role of the knowledge weapon in facing stroke, its symptoms, and complications.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The program is supported by a multi-task team of different medical specialties and nurses available 24 hours a day, seven days a week, carefully qualified to diagnose stroke, rapidly and effectively administer treatment, control symptoms, and minimize complications to the greatest extent possible.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">In addition to our role in stroke treatment, the program provides a full range of outpatient neurology rehabilitation services, including speech problems, occupational therapy and physiotherapy services, in addition to continuous follow-up, high care, and ongoing patient advice, to take care of patients to the fullest.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:37:11','2021-01-01 22:37:11'),(875,'services','title',29,'en',' A comprehensive medical examination program','2021-01-01 22:39:49','2021-01-01 22:39:49'),(876,'services','slug',29,'en','a-comprehensive-medical-examination-program','2021-01-01 22:39:49','2021-01-01 22:39:49'),(877,'services','excerpt',29,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">A medical examination may be the only effort that you must make to ensure yourself good health and to prevent the consequences that may come from a sudden unexpected disease such as breast, colon, and uterine cancer.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 22:39:49','2021-01-01 22:39:49'),(878,'services','content',29,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">A medical examination may be the only effort that you must make to ensure yourself good health and to prevent the consequences that may come from a sudden unexpected disease such as breast, colon, and uterine cancer.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\