l and children in particular, which require early medical intervention to solve the problem.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;If the specialists are not approached promptly, the problems with the child will continue for life, causing psychological symptoms and social problems.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">The Speech Correction and Delayed Speech Clinic at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital is specialized in treating speech problems and communication disorders, this clinic deals with different areas related to speech: language, voice, swallowing, and the auditory system.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:47:17','2021-01-01 22:47:17'),(891,'services','title',33,'en','Depression Treatment Program','2021-01-01 22:49:35','2021-01-01 22:49:35'),(892,'services','slug',33,'en','depression-treatment-program','2021-01-01 22:49:35','2021-01-01 22:49:35'),(893,'services','excerpt',33,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Depression is one of the most common mental disorders in the world, and it is divided into two main types: disorders and Anxiety disorders. </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Both of them spread widely across the globe and greatly affects the mood and feelings of people with it.&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:49:35','2021-01-01 22:49:35'),(894,'services','content',33,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Depression is one of the most common mental disorders in the world, and it is divided into two main types: disorders and Anxiety disorders.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Both of them spread widely across the globe and greatly affects the mood and feelings of people with it. The symptoms of depression vary according to its severity (from mild to severe) and according to the duration of the disease (from months to years), it can be easily diagnosed, and it is worth knowing that it differs from the normal feeling of sadness, stress, and fear that affects every person from time to time in Life.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Globally, 300 million people suffer from depression, representing 4.4% of the world\'s population; unfortunately, this is a relatively high percentage!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Although depression may affect people of all ages and groups, the risk of developing it increases dramatically in the event of poverty, unemployment, or upon the advent of calamities and traumatic accidents such as the death of a relative or loved one, or upon divorce, or physical illness, or Because of the problems that drug and alcohol abuse may cause.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:49:35','2021-01-01 22:49:35'),(895,'services','title',34,'en','Diabetes Control and Treatment Program','2021-01-01 22:52:24','2021-01-01 22:52:24'),(896,'services','slug',34,'en','diabetes-control-and-treatment-program','2021-01-01 22:52:24','2021-01-01 22:52:24'),(897,'services','excerpt',34,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">The Diabetes Control Program 