ult doctors.</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:54:38','2021-01-01 22:54:38'),(902,'services','content',35,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Childbearing problems have always been a sensitive problem in society, as they relate to our children who are the basis and light of life, so parents who suffer from delayed childbearing problems rush to consult doctors.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Al Moosa Childbearing Program offers ample hope to infertile couples. We care about your details and strive to be a reason for your comfort and happiness.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Our specialized medical team understands all the emotional and personal challenges of couples looking for a solution to their infertility problem and is here to help you on your beautiful journey to childbearing.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:54:38','2021-01-01 22:54:38'),(903,'services','title',36,'en','Sickle Cell Anemia Treatment Program','2021-01-01 22:57:08','2021-01-01 22:57:08'),(904,'services','slug',36,'en','sickle-cell-anemia-treatment-program','2021-01-01 22:57:08','2021-01-01 22:57:08'),(905,'services','excerpt',36,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Sickle cell disease is one of the serious diseases that arise as a result of a change in hemoglobin in the blood, and this genetic change causes the secretion of deformed red cells that do not live for the same time as normal red cells, which may lead to their attachment to the blood vessels and cause problems for the patient.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 22:57:08','2021-01-01 22:57:08'),(906,'services','content',36,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Sickle cell disease is one of the serious diseases that arise as a result of a change in hemoglobin in the blood, and this genetic change causes the secretion of deformed red cells that do not live for the same time as normal red cells, which may lead to their attachment to the blood vessels and cause problems for the patient.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">This disease results in painful crises called sickle cell anemia, as well as permanent damage to some vital organs. Sickle cell disease is considered a genetic disease and carriers of this disease inherit two copies of the sickle cell genes (one from the father and the other from the mother), and those who carry one copy (from one parent only) are called the carrier of the sickle cell trait. Something different from sickle cell disease, as a person who carries one gene, does not have the disease but carries one of the genes that cause this disease.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">Sickle cell disease is one of the common diseases in Saudi Arabia, and the premarital screening program estimates that the prevalence of sickle cell trait in adults was 4.2%, and sickle cell disease was 0.26%.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">It was noticed that the highest prevalence of this disease is located in the eastern region, specifically in the city Al-Ahsaa (approximately 17% from sickle cell trait and 1.2% from sickle cell disease).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">The sickle cell disease program provides comprehensive care from various medical specialties to patients with this disease, and our specialized doctors work together in a team spirit to address the challenges that a sickle cell patient may face.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">We also have integrated and interdisciplinary clinics that provide wide services including hematology (for children and adults), other subspecialties in internal medicine (gastroenterology, nephrology, and intensive care unit), and subspecialties of pediatrics, orthopedics, gynecology and obstetrics, general surgery, laboratory, radiology, and anesthesia.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2021-01-01 22:57:08','2021-01-01 22:57:08'),(907,'services','title',38,'en','Migraine Treatment Program','2021-01-01 23:00:28','2021-01-01 23:00:28'),(908,'services','slug',38,'en','migraine-treatment-program','2021-01-01 23:00:28','2021-01-01 23:00:28'),(909,'services','excerpt',38,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Headache is one of the most common diseases that afflict millions of people in the world. Headache affects the daily behavior of a person who suffers it and reduces his productivity at work.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\">&nbsp;</p>','2021-01-01 23:00:28','2021-01-01 23:00:28'),(910,'services','content',38,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Headache is one of the most common diseases that afflict millions of people in the world. Headache affects the daily behavior of a person who suffers it and reduces his productivity at work.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">The causes of headaches differ and the treatment methods differ, and there are many types of headaches such as migraines, cluster headaches, tension headaches, headaches caused by structural problems such as bleeding, vascular diseases, and tumors, all of which we treat at Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, specifically migraine.</span></p>','2021-01-01 23:00:28','2021-01-01 23:00:28'),(911,'service_sections','title',77,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-02 12:14:53','2021-01-02 12:14:53'),(912,'service_sections','title',78,'en','About hair transplantation','2021-01-02 12:17:17','2021-01-02 12:17:17'),(913,'service_sections','title',79,'en','The desired results of a hair transplant procedure','2021-01-02 12:18:30','2021-01-02 12:18:30'),(914,'service_sections','title',80,'en','Are there complications for a hair transplant procedure?','2021-01-02 12:19:34','2021-01-02 12:19:34'),(915,'service_sections','title',81,'en','Can the hair be transplanted into scars?','2021-01-02 12:22:54','2021-01-02 12:22:54'),(916,'service_sections','title',82,'en','Can hair transplant for women?','2021-01-02 12:23:53','2021-01-02 12:23:53'),(917,'service_sections','title',83,'en','Does transplanted hair look natural?','2021-01-02 12:24:46','2021-01-02 12:24:46'),(918,'service_sections','title',84,'en','When can I start styling or shaving hair?','2021-01-02 12:25:20','2021-01-02 12:25:20'),(919,'service_sections','title',85,'en','Before and after hair transplantation instructions','2021-01-02 12:26:30','2021-01-02 12:26:30'),(920,'service_section_items','title',79,'en','Services Provided By The Center','2021-01-02 12:28:26','2021-01-02 12:28:26'),(921,'service_section_items','content',79,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">W</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">e offer many distinctive services at The Hair Transplant Center:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Treating hair loss problems.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Hair transplantation for men and women.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The follicle extraction unit</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Hair transplantation in the area of ​​the face, chin, eyebrows, and mustache.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Hair transplantation in scars resulting from burns and wounds.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:28:26','2021-01-02 12:28:26'),(922,'service_section_items','title',80,'en','About hair transplantation','2021-01-02 12:29:39','2021-01-02 12:29:39'),(923,'service_section_items','content',80,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Hair transplantation is closer to being a simpler medical procedure than being called a surgical procedure, in which the hair follicles are removed from the roots at the back of the head and re-implanted at the front of the head in the place of hair loss. This procedure is performed with local anesthesia of the scalp only, and the person is awake and fully conscious.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We in the hair loss treatment center adopt the follicular unit extraction (FUE) method in our medical procedures, where the device withdraws one hair with its follicle to implant it in the required part, by making very small holes in the desired part, which range from hundreds to thousands of follicles.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Therefore, hair transplantation is considered a relatively long period because these follicles are transplanted one by one.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:29:39','2021-01-02 12:29:39'),(924,'service_section_items','title',81,'en','The desired results of a hair transplant procedure','2021-01-02 12:30:33','2021-01-02 12:30:33'),(925,'service_section_items','content',81,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">After one to two months of hair transplantation, the hair begins to appear after implanting the follicles in the place affected by hair loss, and later, after less than another 6 months, the hair begins to return to the front of the head, as the hair begins to fully grow to its natural length.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:30:33','2021-01-02 12:30:33'),(926,'service_section_items','title',82,'en','Are there complications for a hair transplant procedure?','2021-01-02 12:31:25','2021-01-02 12:31:25'),(927,'service_section_items','content',82,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">There are almost no complications for hair transplantation because the operation is done using local anesthesia, but some infections may occur that can be avoided with antibiotics, and some swelling and bruising may occur in the forehead area, which gradually disappears after a while.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:31:25','2021-01-02 12:31:25'),(928,'service_section_items','title',83,'en','Can the hair be transplanted into scars?','2021-01-02 12:32:13','2021-01-02 12:32:13'),(929,'service_section_items','content',83,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Yes, but it poses many risks since the success rate is less than 80%.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:32:13','2021-01-02 12:32:13'),(930,'service_section_items','title',84,'en','Can hair transplant for women?','2021-01-02 12:32:58','2021-01-02 12:32:58'),(931,'service_section_items','content',84,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Yes, as this type of surgery carries a high success rate.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:32:58','2021-01-02 12:32:58'),(932,'service_section_items','title',85,'en','Does transplanted hair look natural?','2021-01-02 12:34:02','2021-01-02 12:34:02'),(933,'service_section_items','content',85,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Yes, especially when sticking to nutritious foods and natural products of shampoos and creams.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:34:02','2021-01-02 12:34:02'),(934,'service_section_items','title',86,'en','When can I start styling or shaving hair?','2021-01-02 12:34:58','2021-01-02 12:34:58'),(935,'service_section_items','content',86,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Six months after the operation.</span></p>','2021-01-02 12:34:58','2021-01-02 12:34:58'),(936,'service_section_items','title',87,'en','Before and after hair transplantation instructions','2021-01-02 12:41:09','2021-01-02 12:41:09'),(937,'service_section_items','content',87,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">We offer you some important tips after a hair transplant procedure, which would give positive results for the operation and beyond, including:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">General care</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">After the hair transplant surgery, it is recommended that you rest for two days, on the night of the operation and the next day, and you should lie on your back, and try not to go out except for tests during these two days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">On the second or third day of the operation, some swelling and swelling may occur in the face and eyes due to the injections that were injected under the skin for transplantation and nourishment of the transplanted roots, do not worry, this is a normal reaction, and it disappears automatically within 3-5 days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The patient needs to put an ice pack or a cold gel on the forehead and around the eyes for 10 minutes before bed during these three days. This cold gel or ice pack that will be placed on the forehead and the area around the eyes works to remove swelling and puffiness. In addition, the cultivated area should not be exposed to anything for a whole week, and you need to wear a hat in the open air for about two weeks.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 13.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Shower</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The hospital should perform the first wash, or for the doctor to show a video of the washing method and explain it to you, however, if you cannot go to the clinic or hospital, you can wash your head as follows:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">First</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">: Bepanthene lotion is gently applied to the implanted area and left for 30-45 minutes to soften the skin surface.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">After 30-45 minutes, we wash the lotion with water, and then wash the hair with a special shampoo, by lathering a small amount on your hands and then applying it to your hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Second</strong>: Apply shampoo through your fingertips without using nails, then rinse with lukewarm water at room temperature, then dry the hair with a towel.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Third:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"> Apply Fusibact Cream to the donor area and continue applying it for three days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Medicine.</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">After the treatment, you will receive a prescription containing the medicine that you will need to buy and use after the operation, the medicines help to nourish the hair with the necessary substances such as growth factors, and neglecting them may lead to the failure of the process sometimes.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -34.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 31.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Hair Grow</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Within 3 to 12 months of this process, new hair begins to grow. It varies from person to person according to the type of hair, type of metabolism, and adherence to the instructions of the treating doctor.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">At the beginning of hair growth, the hair is thin and weak like the hair of children, and with the progress of time, the hair begins to grow thicker, until it ends with time to be natural hair like adult hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>The average speed of hair growth is 1-8.0cm per month, meaning that your hair will be on average between 5-3cm for 6 months after the procedure.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">The transplanted hair may fall out in the first few months, and after 2-3 months, new hair strands will start to grow and become visible, 40% of hair strands grow between 4-6 months, 60% grow between 6-8 months, and 90% grow between 8- 10 months, and it may take up to a year for you to see full hair growth.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">It is worth noting that the scars on the transplanted area will disappear after about 7-10 days, and during the period of hair growth, blisters may occur, and this is normal in this case, you must make an appointment to visit the clinic or see the treating doctor after the operation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -34.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Headwear, swimming and sports</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">It is best for the first two weeks to have a hat that you wear outdoors and indoors, you should definitely not enter places full of dust, and you can swim as long as you do not wet your hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">You can swim in the sea or swimming pool 15 days after the operation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">It is advised not to do any sports activities during the first three days, after the fourth day, you may start exercising light sports activities such as walking, and it is also advised not to do any other activities within 15 days of the operation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">You can participate in your routine sporting activities two weeks after the operation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">You can participate in contact sports and engage in heavy sports such as football, basketball, etc. after 60 days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 63.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">6.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">All activities that cause excitement, including sex, are completely prohibited for the first three days after the operation, because of their negative effects that may affect the success of the operation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Hair cutting and dyeing</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -34.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 75.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Do not cut your hair during the first two weeks, but your hair can be cut if you want that after the fifteenth day only by a hairdresser trained in cutting the transplanted hair.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -34.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 75.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">When cutting your hair, it is preferable to use scissors for the first two months. Do not use a hair clipper.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -34.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; margin: 12.0pt 0i