n style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>The treatment plan is also prepared in accordance with the patient\'s personal treatment and type of headache, and this includes treatment with a referral to a neurosurgeon. If the origin of the headache is physical problems such as the presence of benign tumors or cancers, treatment can be resorted to with medication.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Do not make headaches a reason to disrupt your daily life and your usual accomplishment; if you have a headache, do not hesitate to consult us, our doctors are here for you!</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:32:47','2021-01-02 13:32:47'),(974,'services','title',39,'en','One-Day Surgery','2021-01-02 13:38:13','2021-01-02 13:38:13'),(975,'services','slug',39,'en','one-day-surgery','2021-01-02 13:38:13','2021-01-02 13:38:13'),(976,'services','excerpt',39,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The science of surgery is one of the largest and most complex sciences of medicine, as it is a science concerned with the minute details in the human body, so this science is one of the sciences that are constantly developing.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:38:13','2021-01-02 13:38:13'),(977,'services','content',39,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The science of surgery is one of the largest and most complex sciences of medicine, as it is a science concerned with the minute details in the human body, so this science is one of the sciences that are constantly developing.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Al-Moosa Specialist Hospital, we were keen to provide a distinguished surgical service through the one-day surgery department, as you can now enter the hospital, undergo surgery, and return home on the same day.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">At Al Moosa Hospital, we are always keen to reduce the length of stay as much as possible, by shifting our operations to the daily surgery department possible, where short-acting anesthesia and advanced surgical techniques are used.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The medical staff, which includes both doctors and nurses, has been trained in the use of health care methods with high training and with a high degree of efficiency and responsibility, which would provide a medical service and health care worthy of the aspirations of our people inside Al-Ahsaa and the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">The biggest advantage in the day surgery department inside Al Moosa Specialist Hospital is that the patient is admitted and discharged on the same day after only a few hours!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">However, you have some cases that may require more hours, up to 24 hours, in some operations, as we will notify the patient in advance.</span></p>','2021-01-02 13:38:13','2021-01-02 13:38:13'),(978,'service_sections','title',98,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:41:16','2021-01-02 13:41:16'),(979,'service_section_items','title',100,'en','Services Provided By The Department','2021-01-02 13:43:07','2021-01-02 13:43:07'),(980,'service_section_items','content',100,'en','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Within the day surgery department, we perform many distinctive operations with high efficiency and in less than one day only, such as:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;\">Urinary Tract.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 8.0pt 22.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" styl