• Gastric balloon insertion for obesity treatment. • pH measurement, esophageal and rectal manometry\nLanguages: Arabic - English\nNationality: Lebanese\nAge group of patients: adults\n','2021-01-03 10:51:18','2021-01-03 10:51:18'),(1761,'blogs','title',11,'en','A VISIT TO A BARBER REVEALS A RARE EGG-SIZED CAROTID SHEATH MASS','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1762,'blogs','slug',11,'en','a-visit-to-a-barber-reveals-a-rare-egg-sized-carotid-sheath-mass','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1763,'blogs','content',11,'en','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">In a 4-hour-procudere</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Segmented Surgical resection of a large odontogenic fibromyxoma</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Grown up or a kid, we all have Dentophobia!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The stereotype of the dentist is always accompanied by the feeling of pain or the needle and other unpleasant treatment procedures.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">So, can you imagine if you were misdiagnosed and your visits to the dentist went to no avail &hellip; with ongoing pain!</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Referred from another hospital, our patient visited Dr. Ibrahim Hassoun, oral and maxillofacial surgery specialist, complains of swelling in the lower jaw with ongoing severe pain, she has been treated for a long time but the pain and swelling were the same, as she was misdiagnosed by her doctors who diagnosed her case with a dental abscess.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Radiological examination with MRI, CT, and conventional radiography pointed to a Neoplasm , so a biopsy was taken for further investigation , the result showed that the patient has a large odontogenic fibromyxoma ,a rare benign neoplasm that mostly affects the posterior region of the mandible, that destroyed her mandibular bone</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The medical team that included, Dr . Ibrahem Hassoun , Dr . Hesham Alsayed , and Dr. Dina Abdul Samee agreed that surgery is the treatment of choice for such rare cases , along with placing a Bone grafting from the iliac bone to prevent the recurrence of the tumor</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The surgery that lasted for 4 hours, was a success and the patient was discharged in good health</span></p>','2021-01-03 11:09:29','2021-01-03 11:09:29'),(1764,'blogs','title',12,'en','BOOSTING MEMORY THROUGH DRAWING','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1765,'blogs','slug',12,'en','boosting-memory-through-drawing','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1766,'blogs','content',12,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">It has long been known that drawing something helps a person remember it.&nbsp;Drawing is superior to reading or writing activities because it forces the person to process information in multiple ways: visually, kinesthetically, and semantically</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The title of a recent documentary film, &ldquo;My Memory Is Better When I Draw,&rdquo; summarizes what research has proven day after day of drawing on cognitive abilities. The film shows how drawing stimulated people&rsquo;s memories with dementia and enabled them to restore their connection with the world. But it seems that this positive effect is not limited to people with dementia, studies have shown that art may be part of treating patients with depression, anxiety, and even cancer, as it allows them to express themselves and their thoughts</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The practice of art has also been associated with improved memory, critical thinking, and flexibility. In healthy elderly.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiase