of the Neuroscience Center at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, Dr. Sherif Saad- Says, &ldquo;Benefit is related to the artistic process and ways to stimulate thinking itself, not the final product or painting.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">The Healing Power of Art.</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-size: 36px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">How Art Heals?</span></h2>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Art is healing because it forces you to forge a connection between your mind and your body. Unlike exercise, which works your body, or meditation, which clears your mind, art-making accesses both mind and body to promote healing. Every time you sit down to write a song or paint a picture, you&rsquo;re using mental processes in a physically engaging activity.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">There is a variety of artistic tools available, from acrylic colors to iPads for people undergoing cancer treatment, and some examples at Harvard University&rsquo;s Massachusetts General Hospital have proven this. The hospital previously worked with former soldiers and Alzheimer&rsquo;s patients; drawing helped them get over their diseases quickly and enjoy their hospital stay.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;Dr. Sherif Saad stated that art has always been able to help people in difficult times, even those who spend most of their free time without specific activities. The doctor adds: &ldquo;Working with a trained art therapist gives patients a way to express themselves in a safe environment, which paves the way for their transition to the next stage of treatment safely. &ldquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-size: 36px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; vertical-align: baseline;\">The protective effect of art</u></span></h2>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">In addition to the healing abilities of art, this treatment method has been shown to have a preventive effect. Recent research indicates that engaging in creative art practice appears to effectively protect from cognitive impairment more than just an artistic appetite for it. It included people over the age of 70; those who participated in craft projects were less likely to develop cognitive impairment as they age than those who read books.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">A 2014 German study that included two groups of retirees found that the group that practiced painting and sculpture showed more significant improvement in spatial perception and emotional flexibility compared to the other group that attended only artistic classes.</span></p>','2021-01-03 11:16:46','2021-01-03 11:16:46'),(1767,'blogs','title',13,'en','NURSING BETWEEN THE SANCTITY OF MISSION AND THE SANCTITY OF DUTY','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1768,'blogs','slug',13,'en','nursing-between-the-sanctity-of-mission-and-the-sanctity-of-duty','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1769,'blogs','content',13,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">A heart beats with Empathy</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">A blast Hit Lebanon days ago. an explosion that wiped out entire streets across the seaside capital, and left us all heartbroken</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Many stories of heroes are beginning to surface &ndash; and this is the tale of the nurse Pamela who pulled three newborns out of a hospital hit by the Beirut blast</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Pamela says &ldquo;we heard a sound then the explosion happened,&nbsp;I was knocked down unconscious, and when I woke up, the whole place was destroyed .The first thing that came to my mind was the&nbsp;newborn&nbsp;triplets;&nbsp;I ran to the nursery, found the three incubators under the rubble, the babies were safe inside , I started removing&nbsp;rubble and metal rods that fell from the ceiling&nbsp; till I reached the babies, I immediately carried them, I was terrified because the incubators&nbsp;were covered with glass and blood- &nbsp;a glass that used to be widows looking at beautiful Beirut &ndash; the voices of the babies&nbsp;crying reassured me that they are still alive. People were trying to also open for us to leave, they opened a small hole that we left through. My only concern was to protect the babies and get them to a safe place, I went down carrying the three babies with no electricity, I was scared one of them would slip&nbsp;from between my arms, especially that I was shacking from fear and trauma, but the hands of Allah were above our hands. &nbsp;I started running towards the nearest hospital, people started taking off clothes and covering the babies as I ran across destruction hearing my heartbeats louder that the scream around me , the smell of death and the yawning of devastated mothers &rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">What hidden force that gave her self-control and the ability to save those children!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">People stand out amidst these violent and dark and these circumstances and this Pamela was up to the task &ndash; how courageous!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">ASH nurses:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Hats off to you all, Pamela is an example reflecting the heroism of you, nurses do not necessarily need to save lives in a dramatic scene to be heroes. In many cases, you are caring for patients with compassion when you unknowingly become heroes to the people around you</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Families go home from the hospital thinking about how you made a tremendous impact on their lives. Yet when you are recognized as heroes, you often say you did not do something special. you were just doing your jobs.&rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">You have qualities that make us astonished, you are not in the shadow , you are &nbsp;the humble leaders and &nbsp;the hope to a better future &ndash; when malls , schools and events were postponed you guys didn&rsquo;t&nbsp; take a break! You risked your own lives to cure patients &ndash; and that is how nurses are meant to be</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Hats off to ASH nurses and all the nurses around the world ..</p>','2021-01-03 11:26:18','2021-01-03 11:26:18'),(1770,'blogs','title',14,'en','SUCCESSFUL AORTIC STENTING FOR A 30-YEAR-OLD PATIENT','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1771,'blogs','slug',14,'en','successful-aortic-stenting-for-a-30-year-old-patient','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1772,'blogs','content',14,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Successful Aortic stenting for a 30-year-old patient</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Our surgical team at Almoosa Specialist hospital led by Dr. Mahmoud Elmeniesy, vascular surgery consultant, managed to save a 30-year-old patient who was suffering from an Aortic dissection.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Dr. Mahmoud stated that the patient came to the hospital in a serious condition suffering from hypertension and severe back and chest pains &ndash; so a medical team from different specialties was formed&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">First, the medical team decided to do a CT scan that showed a dissection in the descending aorta, the largest artery in the body that runs down through the chest and the abdomen.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The team that was consisted of Dr. Elmeinesy, Dr.Samer Qara chief of ICU unit, Dr. Yasser Ghoneim cardiothoracic Consultant, and Dr. Syed Hassan Consultant Interventional Radiology- decided to perform a catheterization to deploy an aortic stent covered the main dissection entry point to prevent possible rupture and fatal bleeding</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The operation was a success, and the patient was discharged in good health, noting that he will continue the follow-ups for six months to check his condition</p>','2021-01-03 11:29:03','2021-01-03 11:29:03'),(1773,'blogs','title',15,'en','COOLED RADIOFREQUENCY ABLATION MODALITY TO TREAT CHRONIC JOINTS PAIN','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1774,'blogs','slug',15,'en','cooled-radiofrequency-ablation-modality-to-treat-chronic-joints-pain','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1775,'blogs','content',15,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Cooled Radiofrequency Ablation Modality to Treat Chronic Joints Pain</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Many people around the world, especially the elderly, are suffering from chronic joints pain, chronic neck pain, and chronic back pain, especially when the surgery is not an option either because of the patient&rsquo;s age or because of having chronic diseases that prevent the patient from having the surgery.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">On the other hand, physicians attempt to offer optimal treatment that is appropriate for all these patients. Here at Almoosa Specialist Hospital, we strive to find innovative treatment solutions that can relieve pain without the need for surgical intervention.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">As the first of its kind on the regional level, the pain management team, led by Dr. Hesham Soliman, an anesthesia consultant and chief of anesthesia and pain management department, and Dr. Osama Al-Attiyah, an anesthesia and pain management consultant, succeed in treating a patient with chronic knee pain using the newest modality of pain management which called cooled radiofrequency ablation.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">What is the cooled radiofrequency ablation modality?</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">It is a minimally-invasive procedure used to treat chronic knee pain in 2-stpes approach:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">First procedure, which is diagnostic: where the medication is injected into the nerves around the knee, which called the Genicular nerves.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;This medication serves to temporarily block the pain signals.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The second step, which is the actual knee radiofrequency ablation</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The Procedure is quite simple and easy. It is a day case procedure where a specialized needle is used to apply heat directly to the nerves of the knee. After this way, it is unable to continue sending pain signals to the brain. The pain relief from this procedure can last up to 2 years or more</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Special things of the cooled radiofrequency ablation that can help with chronic pain include: relieving pain, improving mobility, improving the long-term physical function and quality of life, it is quick to be done, quick recovery time, no overnight hospital stays, and no need for surgical incision.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Lastly, all thanks and appreciation to the pain management team and we wish the patient a good health.</p>','2021-01-03 11:31:44','2021-01-03 11:31:44'),(1776,'menu_items','title',52,'en','Moosa History','2021-01-03 13:41:47','2021-01-03 13:41:47'),(1777,'histories','content',1,'en','<p>The Dream Starts, Boston USA</p>','2021-01-03 13:43:31','2021-01-03 13:43:31'),(1778,'histories','content',2,'en','<p>The First Generation</p>','2021-01-03 13:44:05','2021-01-03 13:44:05'),(1779,'blogs','title',5,'en','‏OFFICE NANOSCOPE ثورة في علاج المفاصل بتقنية النانو سكوب بدون جراحة','2021-01-04 07:18:35','2021-01-04 07:18:35'),(1780,'blogs','slug',5,'en','office-nanoscope-thwrh-fy-alaj-almfasl-btqnyh-alnanw-skwb-bdwn-jrahh','2021-01-04 07:18:35','2021-01-04 07:18:35'),(1781,'blogs','content',5,'en','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">يعتبر مفصل الكتف من أكثر المفاصل مرونة في جسم الإنسان حيث يسمح بأكبر قدر ممكن من الحركة للقيام بالأعمال والأنشطة اليومية. ولكن هذه المرونة تأتي على حساب ثبات المفصل واتزانه مما يجعله الأكثر عرضة للإصابة والخلع&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">خاصة عند الرياضيين. تتسبب مشكلات الكتف الناتجة عن هذه الإصابات في حدوث آلام شديدة ومزعجة، كما انها تؤدي الى تقييد حركة الكتف لفترات طويلة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">وفي انجاز يعتبر الأول من نوعه على مستوى المملكة العربية السعودية، شهد مستشفى الموسى التخصصي بالأحساء نجاح أول عملية تنظير مفصلي باستخدام تقنية النانو سكوب Nanoscope Arthroscopy لمريض في العقد الثالث من العمر يعاني من انحشار وقطع جزئي لوتر الكتف المدورة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">حيث كان المريض يشتكي من الام مزمنة في تلك المنطقة لمدة ثمانية أشهر تحد من حركته وتمنعه من ممارسة حياته الطبيعية. وأوضح الشاب أنه تم علاجه بالأدوية المسكنة ومضادات الالتهابات وجلسات العلاج الطبيعي ولم تتحسن حالته وأصبح التدخل الجراحي هو الحل الأمثل. وبعد اجراء الفحوصات اللازمة قرر الفريق الطبي بإجراء تنظير المفصل باستخدام تقنية النانو سكوب لإنهاء معاناة الشاب وتكللت العملية &ndash; بفضل الله- بالنجاح واسترجع المريض حركه الكتف بشكل جيد بعد العملية مباشرة.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">وبحسب الدكتور نايف الحمام، استشاري جراحة العظام والاصابات الرياضية بمستشفى الموسى التخصصي والذي أجري هذه العملية، إن هذه الطريقة عبارة عن اجراء جراحي حديث ونادر لتشخيص وعلاج امراض الكتف والركبة في نفس&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">الجلسة. حيث يتم الاعتماد في هذه التقنية على استخدام أجهزة وأدوات بأحجام صغيرة جدا &rdquo; بحجم الابرة&rdquo; ذات دقة عالية وتصاميم مبتكرة، وهذا بدوره يساهم في تشخيص وعلاج العديد من حالات العظام بشكل سريع وآمن وبتدخل جراحي أقل.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">يضيف الدكتور الحمام يتم خلال هذه العملية الحديثة عمل ثقب واحد&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">مصغر يتراوح بين ١.٥ الى ١.٩ مل تحت التخدير الموضعي في العيادة</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;ودو</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">ن الحاجة الى غرفة العمليات. يتم بعدها ادخال منظار المفصل للفحص والتشخيص باستخدام كاميرا عالية الجودة، وبمجرد الانتهاء من الفحص يتم اصلاح الاضرار في المفصل وعلاجها بتنظيف الأنسجة التالفة وإزالة النتوء العظمي البارز.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">بينما في جراحة التنظير المفصلي التقليدية -وهي لأكثر شيوعاً حاليا في علاج مثل هذه الحالات- يتم عمل عدة شقوق جراحية يتراوح طولهما ٤مل، أحدهمالمنظار المفصل والآخر للأدوات الجراحية ويخضع المريض خلالها لعملية التخدير العام أو الجزئي في غرفة العمليات في مدة تتراوح بين الساعة الى ساعتين ويحتاج بعدها المريض الى فترة تعافي تتراوح من ثلاث الى ستة أسابيع.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Cairo, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; font-size: 18pt; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">كما أشاد الدكتور نايف الحمام بمميزات هذه التقنية، والتي يمكن وصفها بالثورة العلاجية في عالم جراحة العظام والطب الرياضي، موضحاً بأن مدة العملية تستغرق ما بين ١٠ الى ٣٠ دقيقة ويسمح للمريض بمغادرة المستشفى بعدها وممارسة الحياة الطبيعية والعودة للعمل. ومن مميزاتها أيضا عدم وجود الام ومعدل الاستشفاء فيها أسرع حيث ترجع حركة الكتف الى الحدود الطبيعية في نفس يوم العملية. كما أنها لا تحتاج الى غرز جراحية مما يقلل من حدوث المضاعفات الناتجة عن العملية. وأيضا تعتبر هذه التقنية البديل الأمثل لتصوير الرنين المغناطيسي خصوصا للحالات التي لا يجوز معها استخدام الرنين المغناطيسي، كما لو كان المريض يعاني من رهاب الأماكن المغلقة أو كان هناك اجسام معدنيه في الجسم المراد تصويره.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; outline: 0px; f